title: Vintage Duplex 1BR+Den; Fenced-in Yard, Garage; VIDEO TOUR
posting_body: ['Available for move-in NOW!', 'First floor, 1br+den of an up/down duplex- GORGEOUS UNIT with lots of old-world charm.', 'APARTMENT INFO', '-----------------------------------------------', '-NEW hardwood floors in living room', '-Formal dining room with built-ins', '-Tons of windows', '-Large, sunny kitchen', '-Carpet in bedrooms', '-One large bedroom, one small- PERFECT for a home office!', '-Large, private, front porch', 'LOCATION INFO:', '--------------------------------------------------------------', "- Dayton's Bluff neighborhood; located near I94 and Hwy 52", '- Close to the river, Mounds Park, Metro State, and tons of great restaurants and shops!', 'LEASING INFO', '---------------------------------------', '$45 application fee per applicant', '$1,345 deposit', '$1,345 monthly rent', 'Pets allowed with some restrictions and fees!', '**We screen for evictions and convictions**', 'UTILITIES', '---------------------------------------', 'Residents pay electricity, gas, water/sewer, and optional cable/internet', 'Management pays trash and recycling', 'Free (shared) laundry in basement', 'Parking available out back- garage spot available for $50/mo', 'Check out the video tour:', '<URL>', 'Respond to this add to schedule your showing- EMAIL and online inquiries are the best way to get a hold of us.']
